# Testing and validation

Use focused validation:

```powershell
py -m unittest discover tests
py bot_runner.py --dry-run
py manage_rules.py validate
```

For GitHub Actions or production behavior, verify `BOT_ENABLED`, `BOT_PROFILE`, `BOT_SAFE_MODE`, moderation toggles, and required secrets/variables.
For moderation changes, confirm disabled-by-default and dry-run behavior before considering the change complete.

Keep runtime/log failures visible in stdout, workflow logs, or repo-owned docs.
